                                        <expan>Franken / Francs / Franchi</expan>
                                    </choice> 15.000.000.–) | <choice>
                                        <abbr>Exp.</abbr>
                                        <expan>Expedirt</expan>
                                    </choice> <date when="1871-11-01">1 <choice>
